Installing flask-galatea_contact
================================

Prerequisites
-------------

 * Python 2.7 or later (http://www.python.org/)
 * trytond (http://www.tryton.org/)
 * trytond-galatea

Installation
------------

Once you've downloaded and unpacked the flask-galatea-contact source release,
copy galatea-contact directory in main flask app and rename to contact.

Edit your App flask and register a new blueprint:

from contact import contact
app.register_blueprint(contact, url_prefix='/<lang>/contact')
